 Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Dextrothyroxine, Probucol, Cholestyramine, Ezetimibe, Clofibrate, Colestipol, More', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/299051/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[3] "Product Information. Zepatier (elbasvir-grazoprevir)." Merck & Co., Inc  (2016):', 1767369485);
