, Miconazole, Polymyxin B, Nystatin, Vancomycin, Streptomycin, Rifaximin, Paromomycin, Neomycin', 'Lamivudine, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Rilpivirine, Etravirine, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Cobicistat, More', 'Minor', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/300016/', '[1] "Product Information. Dificid (fidaxomicin)." Optimer Pharmaceuticals  (2011):', 1767369485);
